imdb.title: Bigfoot TV
plot: The latest fashion, entertainment, and nightlife events that happen at or around Bigfoot Studios in Cebu, Philippines. Hosted by two young American actors, watch first hand as they explore Cebu and find out what the island has to offer - from launch parties to feature films.::Jude Moore

The latest fashion, entertainment, and nightlife events that happen at or around Bigfoot Studios in Cebu, Philippines. Hosted by two young American actors, Jude Moore and Emily Trempe, you will be able to watch first hand as they explore Cebu and find out what the island has to offer.::Jude Moore

_Bigfoot TV_ (qv) is where you will see the latest fashion, entertainment, and nightlife events that happen at or around Bigfoot Studios in Cebu, Philippines. Hosted by two young American actors, Jude Moore and Emily Trempe, you will be able to watch first hand as they explore Cebu and find out what the island has to offer! From launch parties to feature films, _Bigfoot TV_ (qv) will have the coverage that will keep you coming back for more. It's our goal to provide interesting and up to date news for everyone to see!::Jude Moore
